{"tid":2209084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色速遞事件 討論區","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T03:57:38.000Z","uid":90520,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"09f5a1deb64f13ff3f576e7309a4bd35c98fd462","tid":2209084,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">黃色經濟圈要擴大 我諗大家都知<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">速遞圈</span>亦都係其中一個重點<br />\n但呢兩日 黃色速遞圈好似發生咗啲事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">傘兵 同 852express 就係當中嘅主角</span></span><br />\n好似係因為 自提點 嘅事有爭執<br />\n詳情都仲未好清楚<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"29029a03d128b3df1f4a836d5f369f930d4879ac","tid":2209084,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"好多黃店都用順豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa23a6505d43a32f258bd81d080091d395e3556","tid":2209084,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:31:00.000Z","msg":"利申 個人覺得 既然本意係想 <span class=\"x-large\">百花齊放</span><br />\n咁當然 所有自提點都可以共用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃圈就係要 召集同路人 同路人互撐嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0ffa1b823df8a908d58796ec960749d828fde3","tid":2209084,"uid":90520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29029a03d128b3df1f4a836d5f369f930d4879ac","tid":2209084,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"好多黃店都用順豐<img src